{"tid":315484,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[基本數學]覺唔覺得「一倍」成日俾人濫用?","createTime":"2017-07-10T05:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:35:40.000Z","uid":48022,"like":529,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8be5b725e6e942d9a3780077ac3476952ba52c","tid":315484,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"例句:<br />\n呢個手袋價錢係你身上果個嘅一倍<br />\n<br />\n實際意思:<br />\n呢個手袋價錢係你身上果個嘅兩倍<br />\n或者<br />\n呢個手袋價錢貴過你身上果個一倍<br />\n<br />\n一倍即係一樣嘅意思,但俾人濫用黎表達兩倍嘅意思,造成數字混淆,實在應該搞清楚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔同意"},{"pid":"fb8dcd61247e30bd33e6be14f490ffff9af7407f","tid":315484,"uid":12853,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過厘個字<br />\n一倍 兩倍同數字上 x2 都一樣 幾奇怪"},{"pid":"0f1499404d8ee10d32c5458d1f8db4b97203e41b","tid":315484,"uid":62722,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"一倍係配埋「多」「少」黎用"},{"pid":"f4915bdafc4551f87f8a40c9ab664ac114b6b999","tid":315484,"uid":35315,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一倍係配埋「多」「少」黎用</blockquote><br />\n正解，完post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5c794a04dcfe40b697ddd923ce9e13f08cf7a0","tid":315484,"uid":48022,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一倍係配埋「多」「少」黎用</blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n好多人唔識基本文法同基本數學而造成混淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da9892dadd94cb43af5bb3d0ee38680614dc19b","tid":315484,"uid":38888,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"貴一倍-----  y x (1+1)<br />\n係兩倍-----  y x (2)<br />\n係一倍-----  y x (1)"},{"pid":"0bff9edde1d338919adfb19529562c7ab33715b6","tid":315484,"uid":34970,"like":